Source.Name: prjxray
Source.Summary: A collection of tools and documentation for Xilinx 7-series FPGAs.
Source.Description: Project X-Ray documents the Xilinx 7-Series FPGA architecture to enable development of open-source tools. The goal is to provide sufficient information to develop a free and open Verilog to bitstream toolchain for these devices.
